title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1728-6.1 - Disposal of excess equipment and supplies
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1728-6.1 - Disposal of excess equipment and supplies

State Regulations

Equipment and supplies which are no longer needed or
useful to the housing company should be disposed of as quickly as
possible. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
1728-6.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
